^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So the point is, on defense I had to come up with a plan to take 6 tricks. I knew from my spade holding that whatever spade holding Wasim had, the spades were favorably placed. And I was worried that diamonds would be pitched on either the @CQ if Wasim had it, or the spades. So I had to adopt an aggressive defense and lead a diamond. |
